<div class="tw-foot p"><div class="fn" id="_fn_p40"><p><strong><a href="#t1-2976958" class="usa-link">Table 1</a>:</strong> Demographics of study providers as well as average appoinments and recorded audit logs in 2016, Study faculty providers were identified based on having worked at the study institution for the first and last two months of 2016 and having seen more than 200 office visits in 2016.</p></div></div></section></section><section id="sec3_2"><h3 class="pmc_sec_title">Validation</h3>
<p>The results of our validation are reported in <strong><a href="#t2-2976958" class="usa-link">Table 2</a></strong>. In total 25 intervals of EHR activity were self-reported, the average reported time was 3.1 ± 3.6 minutes longer than the average time calculated from EHR timestamps (p&lt;.001). On average, each interval had 2.0 ± 2.7 gaps in the audit log where no activity was recorded within the reported interval.</p>
<section class="tw xbox font-sm" id="t2-2976958"><h4 class="obj_head">Table 2.</h4>
<div class="caption p"><p>Validation</p></div>
