<td valign="top" align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">.5 ± .8 (6.9 ± 4.2)</td>
<td valign="top" align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">5.5 ± 5.4 (93.1 ± 4.2)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td valign="top" align="right" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Patient Care With Patient</td>
