</table></div>
<div class="p text-right font-secondary"><a href="table/t4-2976958/" class="usa-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open in a new tab</a></div>
<div class="tw-foot p"><div class="fn" id="_fn_p47"><p><strong><a href="#t4-2976958" class="usa-link">Table 4</a>:</strong> Patient Care is divided into four subcategories: the first three are EHR activity related to open office visits and the fourth is EHR patient related activity outside of an office visit. Time is split further into activity type: modifying and reviewing.</p></div></div></section><p><strong><a href="#t4-2976958" class="usa-link">Table 4</a>:</strong> Patient Care is divided into four subcategories: the first three are EHR activity related to open office visits and the fourth is EHR patient related activity outside of an office visit. Time is split further into activity type: modifying and reviewing.</p>
<p>However, nearly an hour of <em>Patient Care</em> time is spent either on other kinds of encounters such as inpatient encounters or telephone calls, or cannot be easily categorized. In all categories, the vast majority of time was estimated to be spent on reviewing information within the EHR system, with the smallest percentage being 88.2 ± 3.8 % for <em>Patient Care After Patient.</em></p></section><section id="sec3_5"><h3 class="pmc_sec_title">Other Time EHR Use</h3>
<p><strong><a href="#t5-2976958" class="usa-link">Table 5</a></strong> presents the four sub-categories of Other Time. Most Other time is spent on the providers’ homepage (37.9 ± 21.2 minutes per clinic day). In all but one category, 100% of the time was spent reviewing.</p>
<section class="tw xbox font-sm" id="t5-2976958"><h4 class="obj_head">Table 5.</h4>
<div class="caption p"><p>Other Time Allocation</p></div>
<div class="tbl-box p" tabindex="0"><table class="content" frame="box" rules="none">
<thead><tr>
<th valign="top" align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Activity Type</th>
<th valign="top" align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Mean Minutes per Clinic Day</th>
<th valign="top" align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Mean Modify Minutes per Clinic Day (%)</th>
<th valign="top" align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Mean Review Minutes per Clinic Day (%)</th>
</tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td valign="top" align="right" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Dashboard</td>
